<book>
  <chapter xml:id="sect_para1">
    <title xml:id="para1" annotations="font_size:18pt" role="宋体 align_left">
      <emphasis role="pmingliu">道德真經指歸</emphasis>
      能五</title>
    <para xml:id="para2">昔者老子之作《道德經》也，原本形氣，以至<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>神明。性命所始，情意所萌，進退感應，呼吸<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>屈伸，參以天地，稽以陰陽，變化終始，人物<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>所安，窮微極妙，以覩自然。演要伸類，著經<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>二篇，敘天之意，見地之心，將以為國，養物<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>生民。章有表裏，不得易位，章成體備，若本<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>與根。文辭相踐，不可上下，廣被道德，若龍<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>與麟。增一字即成疣贅，損一文即成瘢瘡。<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>自大陳小為之上，紀道論德謂之經。始焉<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>上德不德，化由於道而道不為之主，故授<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>之以昔之得一。昔之得一，動由反行，非有<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>性莫之能聞，故授之以上士。上士性高聰<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>明，深遠獨聞，傲世輕物，唯道是荷，故授之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>以道生一。道生一，至虛無名，稟受混冥，造<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>化清濁，陶冶太和，故授之以天下至柔。天<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>下至柔，纖妙無形，貫堅穿遠，無所不勝，故<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>授之以身有名貨。身有名貨則強大，強大<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>則禍生，故授之以大成。大成若虛，空無名<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>貨，萬物類通，故授之以天下有道。天下有<emphasis annotations="[页码]in">
        <emphasis role="page_num">page=1</emphasis>
      </emphasis>
      <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject><imagedata annotations="[gwdz]in" fileref="/upload/daodejing/Figure-0000-000006.jpeg" width="415pt" depth="285.95pt" format="jpeg"/></imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject>道，在於人君，人君無欲，萬物以存，故授之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>以不出戶。不出戶以知萬民之性命，順受<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>樂安，故授之以為學日益。為學日益，文生<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>事起，傷神害民，故授之以聖人無心。聖人<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>無心，合民之神，慎民性命，歸之素真，故授<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>之以出生入死。出生入死，動損精神，去無<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>歸有，不得長存，故授之以道生之。道生之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>以虛無，無所不存，寂泊不動，無所不然，故<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>授之以天下有始。天下有始，無為是宗，以<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>通萬事，無所不明，故授之以使我有知。使<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>我有知，道修而行，恐失自然，禍及子孫，故<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>授之以善建。善建以德，與物相連，澤及後<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>世，流末繁昌，故授之以含德之士。含德之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>士，體道履神，比於赤子，若無見聞，故授之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>以知者不言。知者不言，陰陽玄化，內以正<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>身，身以及家，家以及人，故授之以政治國。<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>以正治國，無令而行，外方異俗，不制自賓，<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>故授之以方而不割。方而不割，萬物以全，<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>無所不克，天道大光，故授之以治大國。治<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>大國者不可大作大為，大作大為，大亂大<emphasis annotations="[页码]in">
        <emphasis role="page_num">page=2</emphasis>
      </emphasis>
      <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject><imagedata annotations="[gwdz]in" fileref="/upload/daodejing/Figure-0000-000007.jpeg" width="415pt" depth="285.95pt" format="jpeg"/></imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject>動則亡，故授之以大國。大國形便，天下願<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>之，靜下見歸，躁上多兵，故授之以道物。<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>道物之鑿鑿，得之者通，寶之者存，保之者玄，<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>故授之以為無為。為無為則運變無形，不見<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>所治而萬物滋生，故授之以其安易持。<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>未兆易謀，持以若愚，不見所事而百禍自<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>亡，萬福自來，故授之以古之為道。古之為<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>道以愚萬民，絕端滅緒，冥塞知門，故授之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>以江海。江海不知，虛靜處下，以至百谷，故<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>授之以天下謂我大似不肖。不肖之道獨<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>合天心，興師動眾，無敵無勝，故授之以用<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>兵。用兵之理，因天應人，自本而起，不由我<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>心，故授之以吾言易知。吾言易知，無識無<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>明，無言無務，使事自然，故授之以知不知。<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>知不知，去心去意，生而若死，存而若亡，廢<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>我巧態，以逐禍患，故授之以民不畏威。民<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>不畏威，輕禁易入，身陷於司，大命絕天，故<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>授之以勇於敢。勇於敢動其賊心，殺生失<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>理，法廢滅亡，故授之以民不畏死。民不畏<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>死，多欲不禁，適情順意，以至困窮，故授之<emphasis annotations="[页码]in">
        <emphasis role="page_num">page=3</emphasis>
      </emphasis>
      <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject><imagedata annotations="[gwdz]in" fileref="/upload/daodejing/Figure-0000-000008.jpeg" width="415pt" depth="282.55pt" format="jpeg"/></imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject>以人之飢也。人之飢也，重稅多賦，好征營<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>營，堅強躁實，以伐其生，故授之以人之生<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>也。人之生也，柔弱畏敬，和淳纖微，聰明日<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>益，其死也堅強，故授之以天之道。天之道<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>損滿益空，養柔順弱，敗堅破剛，故授之以<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>天下莫柔弱於水。柔弱於水，以至堅強，安<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>微樂小，危以為寧，故授之以小國。小國之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>君，形虛勢弱，懸命於鄰，故授之以信者。信<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>者萬民之所助，而將相之所存，天地之所<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
        <emphasis role="return">
          <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
      </emphasis>祐，而道德之所助也。</para>
    <section xml:id="sect_para3">
      <title xml:id="para3" annotations="font_size:16pt" role="align_both">君平說二經目</title>
      <para xml:id="para4">
        <emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>莊子曰：昔者老子之作也，變化所由，道德<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>為母，效經列首，天地為象。上經配天，下經<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>配地。陰道八，陽道九，以陰行陽，故七十有<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>二。首以陽行陰，故分為上下。以五行八，故<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>上經四十而更始；以四行八，故下經三十<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>有二而終矣。陽道奇，陰道偶，故上經先而<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>下經後；陽道大，陰道小，故上經眾而下經<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>寡；陽道左，陰道右，故上經覆來，下經反往。<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>反覆相過，淪為一形，冥冥混沌，道為中主，<emphasis annotations="[页码]in">
          <emphasis role="page_num">page=4</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject><imagedata annotations="[gwdz]in" fileref="/upload/daodejing/Figure-0000-000009.jpeg" width="415.3pt" depth="287.4pt" format="jpeg"/></imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject>重符列驗，以見端緒。下經為門，上經為戶。<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>智者見其經效，則通乎天地之數、陰陽之<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>紀、夫婦之配、父子之親、君臣之儀，萬物敷<emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>矣。
        <emphasis annotations="[注解2]in">
          <emphasis role="comment2">嚴君平者，蜀郡成都人也，姓莊氏，故稱</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="font_color:#548dd4 [注解换行]in">
          <emphasis role="comment_r">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="[注解2]in">
          <emphasis role="comment2">莊子。東漢章和之間，班固作《漢書》避明</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="[注解2]in">
          <emphasis role="comment2">帝諱，更之為嚴，莊、嚴亦古今之通語。君平</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="font_color:#548dd4 [注解换行]in">
          <emphasis role="comment_r">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="[注解2]in">
          <emphasis role="comment2">生西漢中葉，王莽篡治，遂隱遁煬和，蓋上</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="font_color:#c0504d [定版换行]in">
          <emphasis role="return">
            <emphasis role="pmingliu">r</emphasis>
          </emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="[注解2]in">
          <emphasis role="comment2">世之真</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="font_color:#548dd4 [注解换行]in">
          <emphasis role="comment_r">r</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="[注解2]in">
          <emphasis role="comment2">人也。</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <emphasis annotations="[页码]in">
          <emphasis role="page_num">page=5</emphasis>
        </emphasis>
        <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject><imagedata annotations="[gwdz]in" fileref="/upload/daodejing/Figure-0000-000010.jpeg" width="414.7pt" depth="286.85pt" format="jpeg"/></imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject>
      </para><para/><para/></section>
  </chapter>
